- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as constraint satisfaction problems are commonly used in AI applications. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper involves analyzing the structure of problems and proposing conjectures related to their complexity.
